    "description": "Game is still early in development, updates on Discord &amp; Twitter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/7269591f9ca073b24ef0795db99136d3.avif?t=1713748701\" width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><br>This is SuperCrab Extravaganza!!!<br>You play as Craggy the crab, strongest crab on the beach.<br>Meeting the ocean's spirit you find out that her pearls were stolen.<br>Then brought deep into the ocean by the evil creatures of the sea.<br>Now tasked to return the pearls, your adventure starts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fc54128578a10ad1204585bbfa4667d7.avif?t=1713748701\" width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><br>Wielding powerful claws, you can pinch your enemies and defeat them<br>so that you can progress towards the ocean floor and save the world.<br>But it won't be that easy, as the depths are lurking with perilous creatures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/d1271fb368b7353156eb824da1a390eb.avif?t=1713748701\" width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><br>Planning against the sea spirit, the evil sea titans wanted power.<br>Each stolen pearl holds amazing powers that would make any creature<br>way stronger than the normal fish, even a shard of a pearl can help one<br>swim faster, have thicker skin or have a powerful bite.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/327b7c9f68b20d6b37af027f5ca25c94.avif?t=1713748701\" width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><br>While carrying the pearls, you can use their powers,<br>here is a list of possible powers that will get into the game:<br>Rock element pearl<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Better claws (more damage)<br></li><li>Wall grabbing<br></li><li>Thicker shell(More hit points)</li></ul>Fire element pearl<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fire claw (increased melee range)<br></li><li>Bullet claw (ranged attack)</li></ul>Air element pearl<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stronger legs(double jump)<br></li><li>Swimming flaps(swimming and flying)</li></ul>Water element pearl<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>TBD</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/408bb3c67bb4ed996bd830794ff37003.avif?t=1713748701\" width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><br>The game will have multiple world, each with several levels,<br>Each world will have a boss fight, yielding a shard of pearl or full pearl.<br>While unlocking new powers, some levels have new areas reachable.<br>Are you up for the task? Wishlist now!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/0d40d3b9ddd60ab940fb7588d6d61edf.avif?t=1713748701\" width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183450/extras/fdc56072dbcc1e0f70ad048f7b37c74c.webp?t=1713748701\" width=616 height=45 /></span>",
